Mr. Holmes;;2015;;PG;;Drama,Mystery;;6.9;;Bill Condon;;Ian McKellen,Laura Linney,Hiroyuki Sanada,Hattie Morahan,Milo Parker,Patrick Kennedy,Roger Allam,Phil Davis,Frances de la Tour,Charles Maddox,Takako Akashi,Zak Shukor,John Sessions,Michael Culkin,David Foxxe,Oliver Devoti,Mike Burnside,Nicholas Rowe;;The story is set in 1947, following a long-retired Holmes living in a Sussex village with his housekeeper and her young son. But then he finds himself haunted by a thirty-year old case. Holmes memory isn't what it used to be, so he only remembers fragments of the case: a confrontation with an angry husband, and a secret bond with his beautiful, but unstable wife.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3168230/